reviewText: Whats up with all the classic sports cars I see here?  There a bunch of colorful Porsche roadsters driving around this desert!  I guess it was club or something, but anyway just another added sight in this elusively beautiful area.  I was eager to see what Bike-O-Vision did with this intriguing national park and after seeing the results Im very satisfied.  If youve ever been curious about Joshua Tree or just want a good, even, long-distance-type pace with nice views but not too much change, this video was a good pick.
